Class AbstractFactory

java.lang.Object
fr.polytech.picknpic.persist.AbstractFactory
Direct Known Subclasses:
PostgresFactory
public abstract class AbstractFactory extends Object
An abstract factory class for creating Data Access Object (DAO) instances. Implements the Singleton design pattern to ensure only one factory instance exists. Provides an abstraction for different database implementations (e.g., PostgreSQL).
